comments: Hayes (LAL) establishes himself in a screening position in Murray's (DEN) path and absorbs the contact.  As he releases away to roll, he brings his hands towards Murray and marginal contact occurs.
Jokic (DEN) has his forearm extended and incidental contact occurs with Hayes (LAL) as the two players reach for the loose ball.
Davis (LAL) establishes himself in a screening position and incidental contact occurs when Murray (DEN) moves into the screen.
Davis (LAL) hands the ball off and the resulting contact with Murray (DEN) on the perimeter is marginal.
Jokic (DEN) is in a legal guarding position moving alongside of Reaves' (LAL) path to the basket and incidental contact occurs when Reaves steps into Jokic.
Watson (DEN) maintains verticality and absorbs the body contact that occurs during James' (LAL) driving shot attempt.
Davis (LAL) reaches in as Jokic (DEN) briefly loses control of the ball and the contact is marginal.
A 24-second shot clock violation is whistled before Davis (LAL) gains full possession of the ball.
